@NODE otherservices "OTHER SERVICES "
@{" Main Menu " link Main}

OTHER SERVICES
--------------
I have also written a talk service which is quite similar to this service -
in fact, it was the basis of this conference service. It's something on the
lines of TALK, where this service is similar to IRC.  It will also be
released after a few updates and testing under the latest release of Envoy.

A message (mail) service is currently in the works and will be released
shortly.
       
@{" Main Menu " link Main}
@ENDNODE
 



